      passage: `<p>The World Cup of men&rsquo;s soccer, one of the biggest sporting events on the planet, brought 32 national teams from six continents to the host country, Brazil, in 2014. The event, which is held every four years, has expanded greatly since it was played in Italy in 1934. _____ the World Cup included only 16 teams, most from Europe and the Americas.</p>`,
